dow on itself?\n# Or maybe the sphere is actually dark with just slight illumination\n\n# Let\'s look at the color transition from floor to sphere\nprint("\\nTransition from floor to sphere at x=1200:")\nfor y in range(890, 920):\n    i = (y*w + 1200)*3\n    r, g, b = p[i], p[i+1], p[i+2]\n    print(f"y={y}: ({r:3d},{g:3d},{b:3d})")\nEOF\n'] min_timeout_sec: 15.0 max_timeout_sec: 180.0
